{"lang": "zh_TW", "eventid": "act22side", "eventName": "照我以火", "entryType": "ACTIVITY", "storyCode": "FC-ST-2", "avgTag": "幕間", "storyName": "自灰燼之中", "storyInfo": "跟隨在葦草身邊的塔拉人，大多數決定繼續戰鬥。此時，愛布拉娜與威靈頓公爵正在高速戰艦上眺望，深池大軍已經做好準備。\n", "storyList": [{"id": 0, "prop": "HEADER", "attributes": {"key": "title_test", "is_skippable": "true", "fit_mode": "BLACK_MASK"}}, {"id": 1, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 2, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 3, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 4, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_ltroom", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 5, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 6, "prop": "PlayMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$darkness02_intro", "key": "$darkness02_loop", "volume": 0.4}}, {"id": 7, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 8, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 9, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4017_puzzle_1#1$1", "fadetime": 0.7, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 10, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 11, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......“阿赫茉妮”的間諜身份得以確認，但她安插的情報人員已經全部在掩護下提前撤離。", "name": "菲舍爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_4017_puzzle_1#1$1"}, {"id": 12, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那名感染者的確是另一條德拉克。她的動向已經在我們的掌控之中，只要得到指令，我的部隊會繼續追捕。", "name": "菲舍爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_4017_puzzle_1#1$1"}, {"id": 13, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4017_puzzle_1#10$1"}}, {"id": 14, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......另外，恕我冒昧，請問在屏風後聽取彙報的人，您是頭領，還是......公爵閣下？", "name": "菲舍爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_4017_puzzle_1#10$1"}, {"id": 15, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 16, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_726_1#7$1", "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 17, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 18, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你很敏銳，上一個能指出這一點的孩子，我已經不記得是在幾年前遇見的了。", "name": "開斯特公爵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_726_1#7$1"}, {"id": 19, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "抱歉，我只是想享用完這杯紅茶。請坐過來吧。", "name": "開斯特公爵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_726_1#7$1"}, {"id": 20, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4017_puzzle_1#10$1"}}, {"id": 21, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "菲舍爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_4017_puzzle_1#10$1"}, {"id": 22, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4017_puzzle_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 23, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不，作為感染者，我站在這裡就好。", "name": "菲舍爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_4017_puzzle_1#1$1"}, {"id": 24, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_726_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 25, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你來的時候，看到街角那家小劇院了嗎？", "name": "開斯特公爵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_726_1#1$1"}, {"id": 26, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4017_puzzle_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 27, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是，我看到了......劇院沒有開張，也沒有可疑的人在附近徘徊。", "name": "菲舍爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_4017_puzzle_1#1$1"}, {"id": 28, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_726_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 29, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那是一些自稱塔拉人的藝術家建起的劇院，每晚那裡都會上演基於塔拉文化創作的劇目。", "name": "開斯特公爵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_726_1#1$1"}, {"id": 30, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4017_puzzle_1#10$1"}}, {"id": 31, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......需要我去調查他們嗎？", "name": "菲舍爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_4017_puzzle_1#10$1"}, {"id": 32, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_726_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 33, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不，我很欣賞他們的存在。", "name": "開斯特公爵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_726_1#1$1"}, {"id": 34, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "追捕那條德拉克的事，你不用擔心，我會交給其他人去做。你帶來的情報很有價值，以你的才能，不必把時間消耗在收尾的工作上。", "name": "開斯特公爵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_726_1#1$1"}, {"id": 35, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_726_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 36, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我想請你，為我去特定地點監視威靈頓公爵的行動。", "name": "開斯特公爵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_726_1#7$1"}, {"id": 37, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4017_puzzle_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 38, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......是，感謝您的賞識。", "name": "菲舍爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_4017_puzzle_1#1$1"}, {"id": 39, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_726_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 40, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "對了，之前那個問題，你想好答案了嗎？", "name": "開斯特公爵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_726_1#1$1"}, {"id": 41, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 42, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 1.5}}, {"id": 43, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 44, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 45, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 46, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "34_g1_victoriavillage", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 47, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 48, "prop": "PlayMusic", "attributes": {"key": "$calm_loop", "volume": 0.4}}, {"id": 49, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 50, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 51, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_729_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 52, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哎，信使小姐，你能把信捎多遠？多遠都行？", "name": "受傷的流民"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_729_1#1$1"}, {"id": 53, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那，你能幫忙寫信嗎？", "name": "受傷的流民"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_729_1#1$1"}, {"id": 54, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "就寫幾句話，我只是想跟家裡人說一聲我還活著......", "name": "受傷的流民"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_729_1#1$1"}, {"id": 55, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 56, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 57, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 58, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 59, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "34_g1_victoriavillage", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 60, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 61, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 62, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 63, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1020_reed2_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 64, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "剛剛那位農戶說的，你們應該聽到了。這裡定時會有商隊路過，半小時後就會有一支。", "name": "葦草"}, "figure_art": "avg_1020_reed2_1#1$1"}, {"id": 65, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你們跟著商隊走，能藏進載具的話，最好。靠近橡林郡的地區，應該是威靈頓公爵直屬的領地，他不會容許針對塔拉人的暴行。", "name": "葦草"}, "figure_art": "avg_1020_reed2_1#1$1"}, {"id": 66, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "錯過這次機會的話，會很危險。搜捕隊從附近的移動城市趕到這裡，以最快的速度，應該不用一小時。", "name": "葦草"}, "figure_art": "avg_1020_reed2_1#1$1"}, {"id": 67, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1020_reed2_1#9$1"}}, {"id": 68, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......但你們只要能逃出去，之後的生活就不用太擔心。那些人想要的是我，跟丟了你們的蹤跡之後，他們不會再追的。", "name": "葦草"}, "figure_art": "avg_1020_reed2_1#9$1"}, {"id": 69, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_725_1#4$1"}}, {"id": 70, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "呃，等等......所以，風笛說你是什麼深池的領袖，不是我聽錯了？", "name": "維恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_725_1#4$1"}, {"id": 71, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1020_reed2_1#9$1"}}, {"id": 72, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗯，如果你們之中還有人想要跟著深池戰鬥，可以和我一起，繼續走。", "name": "葦草"}, "figure_art": "avg_1020_reed2_1#9$1"}, {"id": 73, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1020_reed2_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 74, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但深池的身份沒有辦法成為你們的保護傘。之後的路，或許也會像現在一樣......被很多人監視，繼續被人追趕。", "name": "葦草"}, "figure_art": "avg_1020_reed2_1#1$1"}, {"id": 75, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 76, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"fadetime": 0.0}}, {"id": 77, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 78, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_729_1#1$1", "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 79, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 80, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我回來了，嘿。", "name": "受傷的流民"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_729_1#1$1"}, {"id": 81, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我照著你的話跟她說了，說我跟村裡逃出來的人一起，在這邊落腳了，然後編了個石高原野上找不到的地名。", "name": "受傷的流民"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_729_1#1$1"}, {"id": 82, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......可那個信使看起來人挺好的，要是她是真的信使，不是來查我們動向的人，那我不是害得她白跑一趟？", "name": "受傷的流民"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_729_1#1$1"}, {"id": 83, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1020_reed2_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 84, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......我大部分時間，都過著東躲西藏的生活。像她那樣假扮信使的追蹤者，我見過許多。", "name": "葦草"}, "figure_art": "avg_1020_reed2_1#1$1"}, {"id": 85, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_729_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 86, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "唉，好吧。以後還要繼續這麼過。", "name": "受傷的流民"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_729_1#1$1"}, {"id": 87, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_242"}}, {"id": 88, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "別歎氣了，我們抓緊時間分一分手上的物資。", "name": "塔拉流民"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_242"}, {"id": 89, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你這樣受傷了的，就別勉強自己跟著葦草走了。為塔拉人打仗的事，我們幫你。", "name": "塔拉流民"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_242"}, {"id": 90, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_729_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 91, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哈哈，那我這算不算是，已經為塔拉人打過啦......", "name": "受傷的流民"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_729_1#1$1"}, {"id": 92, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_725_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 93, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......葦草，過來過來。", "name": "維恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_725_1#1$1"}, {"id": 94, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我得跟你說件事。", "name": "維恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_725_1#1$1"}, {"id": 95, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 96, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"fadetime": 0.0}}, {"id": 97, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_725_1#1$1", "name2": "char_empty"}}, {"id": 98, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.2}}, {"id": 99, "prop": "characteraction", "attributes": {"name": "right", "type": "move", "xpos": 200.0, "fadetime": 0.3, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 100, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 101, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 102, "prop": "characteraction", "attributes": {"name": "right", "type": "move", "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "false"}}, {"id": 103, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_725_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_1020_reed2_1#9$1", "fadetime": 0.7}}, {"id": 104, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 105, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_725_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_1020_reed2_1#9$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 106, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "本來我是寫在遺書上的，唉，但我活下來了嘛。", "name": "維恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_725_1#1$1"}, {"id": 107, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_725_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_1020_reed2_1#9$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 108, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗯。怎麼了？", "name": "葦草"}, "figure_art": "avg_1020_reed2_1#9$1"}, {"id": 109, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_725_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_1020_reed2_1#9$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 110, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "維恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_725_1#1$1"}, {"id": 111, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_725_1#2$1", "name2": "avg_1020_reed2_1#9$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 112, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......一開始，用鋤頭砸倒那個士兵，害得所有人都得逃跑的人，是我。", "name": "維恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_725_1#2$1"}, {"id": 113, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_725_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_1020_reed2_1#9$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 114, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那天晚上，我見到當兵的在打人，打圖利家的小女兒，就從別人家的牆根抄了一把鋤頭，摸了過去。", "name": "維恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_725_1#1$1"}, {"id": 115, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 116, "prop": "characteraction", "attributes": {"name": "left", "type": "shake", "power": 2.0, "times": 60.0, "fadetime": 0.4, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 117, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.8}}, {"id": 118, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_725_1#6$1", "name2": "avg_1020_reed2_1#9$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 119, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我是不是抖得很厲害？......真對不起，唉。過去這麼久了，我還老是夢見那個場景。", "name": "維恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_725_1#6$1"}, {"id": 120, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "女孩才十四歲，尖聲尖氣的，哭得讓人心慌。", "name": "維恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_725_1#6$1"}, {"id": 121, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我想，天那麼黑，也不許點燈，就算這一鋤頭砸破了頭，流了血，樣子再怎麼慘，我也看不清楚。", "name": "維恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_725_1#6$1"}, {"id": 122, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_725_1#5$1", "name2": "avg_1020_reed2_1#9$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 123, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我就是......我沒想到害了那麼多人。", "name": "維恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_725_1#5$1"}, {"id": 124, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "後來我想陪著他們，給所有人想辦法安頓下來，自己再離開，算是償還我犯的錯......", "name": "維恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_725_1#5$1"}, {"id": 125, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_725_1#6$1", "name2": "avg_1020_reed2_1#9$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 126, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "可是有的人最後也沒能走到落腳的地方。", "name": "維恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_725_1#6$1"}, {"id": 127, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_725_1#6$1", "name2": "avg_1020_reed2_1#6$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 128, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......證件不齊的罪名，是你給自己編的嗎？", "name": "葦草"}, "figure_art": "avg_1020_reed2_1#6$1"}, {"id": 129, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_725_1#6$1", "name2": "avg_1020_reed2_1#6$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 130, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "唉，對不起。", "name": "維恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_725_1#6$1"}, {"id": 131, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "一開始通緝令上面沒有我，我怕他們起疑心，才特地跟費加爾一塊去搶藥店......結果又把你也牽扯進來。", "name": "維恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_725_1#6$1"}, {"id": 132, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_725_1#6$1", "name2": "avg_1020_reed2_1#1$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 133, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不要這麼說，維恩。我的身份，總有一天會追上我。", "name": "葦草"}, "figure_art": "avg_1020_reed2_1#1$1"}, {"id": 134, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_725_1#6$1", "name2": "avg_1020_reed2_1#2$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 135, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......塔拉人的悲哀，也總有一天會追上每個人。", "name": "葦草"}, "figure_art": "avg_1020_reed2_1#2$1"}, {"id": 136, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_725_1#6$1", "name2": "avg_1020_reed2_1#2$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 137, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......好，好，唉。", "name": "維恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_725_1#6$1"}, {"id": 138, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 139, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"fadetime": 0.5}}, {"id": 140, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 141, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_725_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_728_1#1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 142, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哎，莫蘭，你想不想......", "name": "維恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_725_1#1$1"}, {"id": 143, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_725_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_728_1#1$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 144, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "怎麼了，維恩？", "name": "莫蘭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_728_1#1$1"}, {"id": 145, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_725_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_728_1#1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 146, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......不，沒什麼。繩子給我吧，我來捆，你這樣帶著行李走不遠。", "name": "維恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_725_1#1$1"}, {"id": 147, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_725_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_728_1#6$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 148, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "呵呵，你是行家。", "name": "莫蘭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_728_1#6$1"}, {"id": 149, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_725_1#6$1", "name2": "avg_npc_728_1#6$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 150, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你也要跟著葦草繼續打仗？", "name": "維恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_725_1#6$1"}, {"id": 151, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_725_1#6$1", "name2": "avg_npc_728_1#6$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 152, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗯。塞爾蒙說，我很有力氣，應該可以做不少事。", "name": "莫蘭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_728_1#6$1"}, {"id": 153, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_725_1#6$1", "name2": "avg_npc_728_1#6$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 154, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......可你在黑的地方就看不見東西，多不方便。", "name": "維恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_725_1#6$1"}, {"id": 155, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "而且，那可是打仗啊，要面對的敵人肯定比我們那天晚上見到的更多，更厲害。", "name": "維恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_725_1#6$1"}, {"id": 156, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "還有大炮。打仗不是那種被砍一刀流點血的事，不是戲裡面演的那樣，英雄被打倒，還能爬起來。人會一下子就死掉，死得很難看......", "name": "維恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_725_1#6$1"}, {"id": 157, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_725_1#6$1", "name2": "avg_npc_728_1#1$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 158, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......但是我想選這條路。", "name": "莫蘭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_728_1#1$1"}, {"id": 159, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_725_1#6$1", "name2": "avg_npc_728_1#6$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 160, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我想，抓住我生活裡難得的選擇機會。", "name": "莫蘭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_728_1#6$1"}, {"id": 161, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1020_reed2_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 162, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "商隊靠近了。", "name": "葦草"}, "figure_art": "avg_1020_reed2_1#1$1"}, {"id": 163, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_725_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 164, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "好，我去和他們交涉，把受傷的人送走。", "name": "維恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_725_1#1$1"}, {"id": 165, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "維恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_725_1#1$1"}, {"id": 166, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_725_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 167, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "維恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_725_1#2$1"}, {"id": 168, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_725_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 169, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "葦草......我能走嗎？", "name": "維恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_725_1#6$1"}, {"id": 170, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "現在的我，能離開了嗎？", "name": "維恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_725_1#6$1"}, {"id": 171, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 172, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 173, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 174, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 175, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 176, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_black", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 177, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 178, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 179, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 180, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我想，一切都已經準備好了。"}}, {"id": 181, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "只剩下......我的妹妹，她還在外彷徨，但她終究會做出正確的選擇。"}}, {"id": 182, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 183, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 184, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 185, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 186, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "34_g11_hispdwarshipdeck", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 187, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 188, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$darkness01_intro", "key": "$darkness01_loop", "volume": 0.4}}, {"id": 189, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 190, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 191, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "“加斯特里爾”號高速戰艦甲板"}}, {"id": 192, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 193, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_652_1#8$1", "name2": "avg_npc_722_1#1$1", "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 194, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 195, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_652_1#8$1", "name2": "avg_npc_722_1#1$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 196, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "曾經最龐大的移動城市上抽離的一根骸骨，搭載維多利亞軍工技術純粹的結晶，多少人該以登上這艘高速戰艦為榮。", "name": "愛布拉娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_722_1#1$1"}, {"id": 197, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "縱使放眼整片泰拉大地，我想也不會有能與此媲美的軍事機器。", "name": "愛布拉娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_722_1#1$1"}, {"id": 198, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_652_1#8$1", "name2": "avg_npc_722_1#1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 199, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "若非如此，它便配不上德拉克麾下傳奇將領之名。", "name": "威靈頓公爵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_652_1#8$1"}, {"id": 200, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_652_1#8$1", "name2": "avg_npc_722_1#6$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 201, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "也有許多人一直窺探著它的動向，試圖從中揣摩您的立場......", "name": "愛布拉娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_722_1#6$1"}, {"id": 202, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_652_1#8$1", "name2": "avg_npc_722_1#1$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 203, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在長達七年的巡遊之後，今天該是它靠岸的日子了。", "name": "愛布拉娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_722_1#1$1"}, {"id": 204, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 205, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"fadetime": 0.0}}, {"id": 206, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_652_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 207, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們轉向後，有多少信使正在回報訊息的路上？", "name": "威靈頓公爵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_652_1#1$1"}, {"id": 208, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_241"}}, {"id": 209, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "除了開斯特公爵，各位公爵都在保持關注，但他們掌控下的任何一支軍隊都已經來不及干預。", "name": "維多利亞軍官"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_241"}, {"id": 210, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "橡林郡已經停止行駛，做好接駁準備。雖然這是本艦七年來首次靠近一座移動城市，但停留過程中，並無過多資源補給和機械維護需求。", "name": "維多利亞軍官"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_241"}, {"id": 211, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "伯爵表示，屆時會親自前往港口迎接您。", "name": "維多利亞軍官"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_241"}, {"id": 212, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 213, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"fadetime": 0.0}}, {"id": 214, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_652_1#8$1", "name2": "avg_npc_722_1#1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 215, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那些踟躕不前的阿斯蘭附庸，恐怕到這艘艦船徑直駛向橡林郡的時刻才會發現，這座城市究竟權屬歸誰。", "name": "威靈頓公爵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_652_1#8$1"}, {"id": 216, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_652_1#8$1", "name2": "avg_npc_722_1#1$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 217, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "而這裡將再次升起怎樣的火焰，他們還一無所知。", "name": "愛布拉娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_722_1#1$1"}, {"id": 218, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "深池的軍隊，那些渴望從不公中解脫的塔拉人，已經從維多利亞各處趕來。", "name": "愛布拉娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_722_1#1$1"}, {"id": 219, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我的謀臣......她做得很不錯。", "name": "愛布拉娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_722_1#1$1"}, {"id": 220, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 221, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"fadetime": 0.0}}, {"id": 222, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_652_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 223, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我的城市，是否停在了我期望的地點？", "name": "威靈頓公爵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_652_1#1$1"}, {"id": 224, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_241"}}, {"id": 225, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是。受限於地形與安全因素，這就是城市航道上最靠近廢城遺跡的位置。", "name": "維多利亞軍官"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_241"}, {"id": 226, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_652_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_722_1#1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 227, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "您怎麼看，愛布拉娜殿下？在前來的路上，您造訪過那處遺址。", "name": "威靈頓公爵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_652_1#1$1"}, {"id": 228, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_652_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_722_1#1$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 229, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我想這樣就夠了。無論塔拉文化的復興者將多少想像寄託在蓋爾王的王城上，那終究只是一處衰朽的廢墟。", "name": "愛布拉娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_722_1#1$1"}, {"id": 230, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "屆時那些浪漫的夢想家只需要透過原野的晨霧，朝它的方向投去一瞥，知道它曾經矗立在山丘上而如今已經被天災損毀，就夠了。", "name": "愛布拉娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_722_1#1$1"}, {"id": 231, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_652_1#8$1", "name2": "avg_npc_722_1#1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 232, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我聽說，塔拉王朝覆滅、德拉克族裔出逃後，阿斯蘭們放任那座石城空置，直到它在天災中坍塌，幾乎被塔拉人遺忘。", "name": "威靈頓公爵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_652_1#8$1"}, {"id": 233, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_652_1#8$1", "name2": "avg_npc_722_1#6$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 234, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那古舊王朝的殘餘......原本也十分無趣。", "name": "愛布拉娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_722_1#6$1"}, {"id": 235, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "維多利亞的君主分封的蓋爾王頭銜，不過是僕臣的美稱。要是留有王冠，我就要將它熔毀；要是尚有王座，我就要將它一把火燒成灰燼。", "name": "愛布拉娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_722_1#6$1"}, {"id": 236, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不過，那裡卻連這些都不剩了。", "name": "愛布拉娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_722_1#6$1"}, {"id": 237, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_652_1#8$1", "name2": "avg_npc_722_1#6$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 238, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "因此那位年輕的沃里克，從蓋爾王的傳說開始找回塔拉的歷史，不是壞事。", "name": "威靈頓公爵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_652_1#8$1"}, {"id": 239, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_652_1#8$1", "name2": "avg_npc_722_1#1$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 240, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "您說的是那位“頌古者”沃里克，“北方戰線的沃里克”？......啊，您認識他？", "name": "愛布拉娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_722_1#1$1"}, {"id": 241, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_652_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_722_1#1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 242, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我曾向他的宴會派出使者。這艘戰艦的巡遊正是從那時開始。", "name": "威靈頓公爵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_652_1#1$1"}, {"id": 243, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_652_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_722_1#1$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 244, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "您一向高瞻遠矚。", "name": "愛布拉娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_722_1#1$1"}, {"id": 245, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_652_1#8$1", "name2": "avg_npc_722_1#1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 246, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這不算多麼長久的等待。", "name": "威靈頓公爵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_652_1#8$1"}, {"id": 247, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_652_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_722_1#1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 248, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "橡林郡......您想去看看這座城市嗎？", "name": "威靈頓公爵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_652_1#1$1"}, {"id": 249, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_652_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_722_1#1$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 250, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "當然。我很好奇，在那場大火後，它被重塑成了什麼模樣。", "name": "愛布拉娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_722_1#1$1"}, {"id": 251, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_652_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_722_1#6$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 252, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "畢竟，它曾經是我的家鄉。", "name": "愛布拉娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_722_1#6$1"}, {"id": 253, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 254, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 1.5}}, {"id": 255, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 256, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 257, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 258, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_black", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 259, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 260, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$burningloop1", "volume": 0.6, "loop": "true", "channel": "kfire"}}, {"id": 261, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 262, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 263, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我握著姐姐的長槍，站在走廊上等了一會。"}}, {"id": 264, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "府邸裡的每個人都沉默地低著頭，刻意忙碌著，一旦看到我就移開視線。"}}, {"id": 265, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "老師的身體一直不好，晚上冒著風雪從宴會回來後就沒有離開過自己的房間。戴莉醫生為他準備了甜酒，卻沒有按時來取走空杯。"}}, {"id": 266, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "門縫中傳出細小的木頭爆裂聲。雪夜的爐火應該很溫暖，此刻火焰平靜燃燒的聲音卻令我牙齒打顫。"}}, {"id": 267, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我還是推開了門。"}}, {"id": 268, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 269, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$rebel_intro", "key": "$rebel_loop", "volume": 0.4}}, {"id": 270, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_open_door", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 271, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 272, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.8, "g": 0.8, "b": 0.8, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 273, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {"image": "34_i11", "screenadapt": "coverall", "fadetime": 0.0}}, {"id": 274, "prop": "ImageTween", "attributes": {"xFrom": 0.0, "yFrom": 0.0, "xTo": 230.0, "xScaleFrom": 1.6, "yScaleFrom": 1.4, "xScaleTo": 1.4, "yScaleTo": 1.4, "duration": 0.5, "block": "false"}}, {"id": 275, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 276, "prop": "soundvolume", "attributes": {"channel": "kfire", "volume": 1.0, "fadetime": 4.0}}, {"id": 277, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 3.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 278, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 279, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......既然你已經說服所有人背叛了我......那這杯甜酒，我為什麼不喝呢？", "name": "沃里克伯爵"}}, {"id": 280, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我以為，您會想知道自己哪裡有過失，才導致您的僕從們求助於我。", "name": "愛布拉娜"}}, {"id": 281, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "咳咳......這不重要，愛布拉娜......", "name": "沃里克伯爵"}}, {"id": 282, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "重要的是，你能使他們，一直信你嗎？", "name": "沃里克伯爵"}}, {"id": 283, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "啊，當然。", "name": "愛布拉娜"}}, {"id": 284, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "您也不問，為什麼我願意答應他們。", "name": "愛布拉娜"}}, {"id": 285, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "咳......你知道，我死後，這座城市會發生什麼嗎？", "name": "沃里克伯爵"}}, {"id": 286, "prop": "ImageTween", "attributes": {"xFrom": 230.0, "xTo": 0.0, "yTo": 0.0, "xScaleFrom": 1.4, "yScaleFrom": 1.4, "xScaleTo": 1.0, "yScaleTo": 1.0, "duration": 30.0, "block": "false"}}, {"id": 287, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "貴族間的力量會失衡，菲力普伯爵在議會上的發言不會再有人反對，但為了得到斯塔福德公爵的重視，那兩位年輕的男爵會在暗中動手。", "name": "愛布拉娜"}}, {"id": 288, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "與此同時，剛剛找回姓名的塔拉人會失去他們的領袖與庇護者。", "name": "愛布拉娜"}}, {"id": 289, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他們會在嚴苛的法令與貴族的反復無常之間被翻攪，蹂躪，直到......忍無可忍。", "name": "愛布拉娜"}}, {"id": 290, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但即使您活著，那一切流血、暴力與動亂，也遲早會發生。", "name": "愛布拉娜"}}, {"id": 291, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我說得對嗎，老師？", "name": "愛布拉娜"}}, {"id": 292, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "呵呵......到了那時候，你會如何做？", "name": "沃里克伯爵"}}, {"id": 293, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我會......伸手將他們從灰燼中拉起來。", "name": "愛布拉娜"}}, {"id": 294, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "拉芙希妮"}}, {"id": 295, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 296, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 297, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "老師失去血色的臉上，不知為何浮現了欣慰的笑容。"}}, {"id": 298, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "貪婪的德拉克，野心無窮無盡的德拉克......我半生的搜尋，沒有找錯......呼......", "name": "沃里克伯爵"}}, {"id": 299, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他摘下眼鏡，緩慢而艱難地轉頭，望向大雪紛飛的窗外。"}}, {"id": 300, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "十年前的冬夜，他念完傳奇小說，手指撫過書脊上燙金的塔拉字母時，也曾露出那樣眷戀又期盼的眼神。"}}, {"id": 301, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我看到......屬於塔拉的新時代......近在眼前。", "name": "沃里克伯爵"}}, {"id": 302, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "可是......", "name": "沃里克伯爵"}}, {"id": 303, "prop": "multiline", "attributes": {"name": "沃里克伯爵", "delay": 0.02, "content": "拉芙希妮啊......"}}, {"id": 304, "prop": "multiline", "attributes": {"name": "沃里克伯爵", "delay": 0.02, "content": "還有......"}}, {"id": 305, "prop": "multiline", "attributes": {"name": "沃里克伯爵", "end": "true", "content": "你......", "joined": "拉芙希妮啊......還有......你......"}}, {"id": 306, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我一動不動地站在門口。玻璃窗上，映出的是我被冰冷的火焰照亮的臉。"}}, {"id": 307, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "如此惶恐，卻與那副憐憫的面孔，一模一樣。"}}, {"id": 308, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......拉芙希妮，你會是誰的學生？"}}, {"id": 309, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 310, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 311, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 312, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 313, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 314, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 315, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": ""}}], "OPTIONTRACE": true}